examples.en: Cost-cutting has led to a lower quality of service.
100 workers are facing the axe in a cost-cutting exercise.
The governor has proposed a number of cost-cutting measures.
Cutting costs is the only solution.
They are cutting costs by using nonunion labor.
The decision was made with the object of cutting costs.
The director has launched out on yet another plan for cutting costs.
Cost cutting had enabled the organization to survive a previous cash crunch.
